    "description_long": "This is a silver Mercedes-Benz convertible car with a sleek, aerodynamic body and a two-door design. The vehicle features a prominent Mercedes-Benz emblem on the front grille, clear headlamps, and a low, sporty stance. The interior is open, revealing two front seats and a rear seating area, with the roof retracted to expose the cabin. The wheels are multi-spoke alloys, and the car has detailed side mirrors and door handles. The rear of the car displays classic taillights and a visible license plate. The overall design suggests a luxury sports convertible, ideal for urban and suburban environments.",
